    <item>
      <title>由于能源援助被取消，欧元区通胀再次上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/euro-area-inflation-bounces-back-as-energy-aid-is-phased-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月份欧元区通胀加速，突显了欧洲央行预计，随着各国政府取消对高能源成本的支持，重返 2% 的道路将崎岖不平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/euro-area-inflation-bounces-back-as-energy-aid-is-phased-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的中国影子银行中植申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/troubled-china-shadow-bank-zhongzhi-files-for-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国影子银行巨头中植企业集团有限公司申请破产，这家公司在巅峰时期管理着超过1400亿美元的资产，随后又陷入对世界第二大经济体造成严重破坏的房地产危机，从而加速了公司的迅速垮台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/troubled-china-shadow-bank-zhongzhi-files-for-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 09:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业报告公布前欧洲股市新年暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/european-stocks-resume-their-slump-ahead-of-key-us-jobs-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四短暂喘息后，欧洲股市进一步下跌，投资者关注重要的美国就业报告，该报告将有助于衡量美联储降息的时机和步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/european-stocks-resume-their-slump-ahead-of-key-us-jobs-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 08:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国调查欧盟白酒，贸易争端加剧导致股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/china-starts-anti-dumping-probe-on-brandy-from-eu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在对来自欧盟的白兰地等酒类产品发起反倾销调查，这是继去年秋天欧盟对其电动汽车补贴展开调查之后采取的相对温和的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/china-starts-anti-dumping-probe-on-brandy-from-eu</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国就业数据公布之前，债券和股票继续下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/stocks-bonds-fall-as-investors-pare-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于劳动力市场的弹性可能会推迟美联储降息的猜测，美国国债延续跌势，将出现 10 月份以来最大单周回落。股市下跌，美元连续第六天走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/stocks-bonds-fall-as-investors-pare-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
